parent1.code: A mesmerizing watercolor of three iridescent hummingbirds in the style of surrealist magical realism. They gracefully hover around a colossal bioluminescent flower in a mystical rainforest at twilight, delicately sipping shimmering nectar from its translucent petals, with enchanted fireflies and prismatic orbs illuminating the dreamlike scene.

offspring.code: A captivating watercolor of three lustrous, gossamer-winged hummingbirds in the style of ethereal surrealist magical realism. They effortlessly pirouette around a colossal bioluminescent flower in the misty, mystical rainforest at twilight, delicately sipping shimmering nectar from its undulating petals, with enchanted fireflies and iridescent orbs illuminating the dreamlike scene.
